        "sourceUri": "file:///Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph/docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "sourcePath": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph/docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "codebasePath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md#L88",
        "lineStart": 88,
        "lineEnd": 88,
        "sourceSha256": "0c1b97376988dd437d0975f1190cc93ff26d02c77abcae7e43efb321ddabff0f"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document:table:90:1",
      "@type": "Table",
      "labels": [
        "Table"
      ],
      "name": "Table 1",
      "chunk_text": "| Interaction | Trigger | Effect | Stability Constraint |\n|------------|---------|--------|----------------------|\n| Select node | Click node | Store selection updates | Must not trigger full scene rebuild unnecessarily |\n| Select edge | Click edge | Store selection updates | Must not invalidate layout caches |\n| Context menu | Right click canvas | Open props/actions | Must cleanup listeners on close/unmount |\n| Markdown text selection | Click / double click / triple click in Viewer/Presentation | Native selection only (caret anchor / word / paragraph) | Must not hijack native selection gestures |\n| Markdown “Show on/in …” | Right click in Editor/Viewer/Presentation | Open Selection Toolbar at exact pointer position | Must not “fly out”; must not use Monaco default context menu |\n| Markdow",
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "| Interaction | Trigger | Effect | Stability Constraint |\n|------------|---------|--------|----------------------|\n| Select node | Click node | Store selection updates | Must not trigger full scene rebuild unnecessarily |\n| Select edge | Click edge | Store selection updates | Must not invalidate layout caches |\n| Context menu | Right click canvas | Open props/actions | Must cleanup listeners on close/unmount |\n| Markdown text selection | Click / double click / triple click in Viewer/Presentation | Native selection only (caret anchor / word / paragraph) | Must not hijack native selection gestures |\n| Markdown “Show on/in …” | Right click in Editor/Viewer/Presentation | Open Selection Toolbar at exact pointer position | Must not “fly out”; must not use Monaco default context menu |\n| Markdown apply + toggle | Cmd/Ctrl+Enter in Markdown section | Apply (when in Editor) and toggle Editor↔Viewer | Must be scoped to BottomPanel Markdown root (no global hijack) |\n| Pan/zoom | Drag/scroll | Update viewport transform | Must keep updates throttled and stable |\n| 2D zoom parity | Wheel / trackpad pinch | D3 / Flow / Flow Editor must share one SSOT wheel normalization + sensitivity | Forbid per-renderer ad-hoc wheel scaling or passive wheel handlers that allow page scroll |\n| Flow drag safety | Pointer drag on Flow/Flow Editor | Disable text selection and browser dragstart during canvas interactions | Forbid selection/copy cursors or panel text selection while pointer is captured |\n| Viewport metrics | Toolbar → Status | Open Status Panel that surfaces zoom/pan/selection/renderer metrics | Forbid floating HUD/status duplication; keep one SSOT surface |\n| Toast notification | Store adds toast | Surface transient status/errors | Must not overlap; newest stays at default Y and pushes older downward |",
        "order": 1
      },
      "metadata": {
        "parsedAt": "2026-04-16T15:31:10+00:00",
        "source": "knowgrph_parser.graph_builder",
        "codebaseRoot": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph",
        "codebaseRelPath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
