    {
      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document:table:108:1",
      "@type": "Table",
      "labels": [
        "Table"
      ],
      "name": "Table 1",
      "chunk_text": "| Context | Intent | Directive |\n|---------|--------|-----------|\n| UI Controls | Keep icon+text rows visually stable | - [ ] Use `inline-flex items-center` for icon+text; forbid baseline drift from mixed inline layout |\n| Icons (Lucide) | Align icon glyphs with text | - [ ] Apply shared icon baseline alignment; forbid per-component ad-hoc offsets |\n| SVG Labels | Keep label center alignment consistent | - [ ] Anchor and baseline-align SVG text; forbid default-anchor mismatches that overlap nodes |\n| Titles & ellipsis | Keep long titles readable and stable | - [ ] Render long titles truncated with ellipsis at rest; on inline edit, reuse typography and reveal full text via horizontal scroll; forbid alternate WYSIWYG title stacks or layout/spacing drift when entering edit |",
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "| Context | Intent | Directive |\n|---------|--------|-----------|\n| UI Controls | Keep icon+text rows visually stable | - [ ] Use `inline-flex items-center` for icon+text; forbid baseline drift from mixed inline layout |\n| Icons (Lucide) | Align icon glyphs with text | - [ ] Apply shared icon baseline alignment; forbid per-component ad-hoc offsets |\n| SVG Labels | Keep label center alignment consistent | - [ ] Anchor and baseline-align SVG text; forbid default-anchor mismatches that overlap nodes |\n| Titles & ellipsis | Keep long titles readable and stable | - [ ] Render long titles truncated with ellipsis at rest; on inline edit, reuse typography and reveal full text via horizontal scroll; forbid alternate WYSIWYG title stacks or layout/spacing drift when entering edit |",
        "order": 1
      },
